{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e25c6cc05","title":"在中共中央书记处会议上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a1ec3275f9","index":0,"year":1944,"month":4,"day":15,"articleId":"8e25c6cc05"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji18","name":"毛泽东全集第18卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji18.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji18":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"427e79d47f","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央书记处会议上的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"8e25c6cc05"},{"id":"a9e751e618","type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年4月15日）这次总的态度是不单不六，表示我们要求和缓，要求抗战到底，团结到底，不表示盛气凌人的态度。我们要求与他们一同抗日，使他们不感觉我们威胁他们。对中间派主要是宣传民主，争取他们的同盟。对英、美主要是宣传抗战，要求英、美派人常驻陕甘宁边区。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"8e25c6cc05"}],"page":{"id":"fbe574cab1","publicationId":"maoquanji18","articleId":"8e25c6cc05","start":436,"end":436}}}},"__N_SSG":true}